---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="site-footer" id="contact">
	<section class="newsletter" id="newsletter" aria-labelledby="newsletter-title">
		<div class="newsletter__inner" data-reveal>
			<p class="eyebrow">ΜΕΙΝΕΤΕ ΣΤΟΝ ΡΥΘΜΟ ΤΗΣ ΕΥΕΞΙΑΣ</p>
			<h2 id="newsletter-title">Γίνετε μέλος της κοινότητάς μας</h2>
			<p>Ενημερωθείτε με τα τελευταία νέα μας</p>
			<form action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST">
				<label for="newsletter-email">Email</label>
				<div class="newsletter__form-row">
					<input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="2f02a73c-297c-4978-b6ed-c64478123128">
					<input
						id="newsletter-email"
						type="email"
						name="email"
						autocomplete="email"
						placeholder="Το email σας"
						required
					/>
					<button class="button" type="submit">Εγγραφή</button>
				</div>
			</form>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="footer-main">
		<div class="footer-grid">
			<section class="footer-brand" aria-labelledby="footer-brand-title">
				<svg class="footer-brand__line-art" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 220 290">
					<path d="M149 30c-21 1-36 16-38 37-2 18 7 33 3 48-5 18-22 22-34 37-19 24-16 63-2 91 10 20 28 34 49 37"></path>
					<path d="M113 68c15 10 33 9 47 1-2 17-14 31-31 35"></path>
					<path d="M82 145c-29 18-49 50-51 86-1 22 6 40 21 50"></path>
					<path d="M109 149c20 30 22 67 7 101-5 12-12 23-21 31"></path>
				</svg>
				<h2 id="footer-brand-title">Enterlife</h2>
				<p>
					H ιστοσελίδα που ασχολείται με την τεχνολογία και την ευεξία, ασκώντας το πνεύμα με το σώμα σύμφωνα με τις ρήσεις των αρχαίων Ελλήνων,
					Νοῦς ὑγιὴς ἐν σώματι ὑγιεῖ.
				</p>
				<a class="text-link" href="#articles">Διαβάστε άρθρα</a>
			</section>

			<nav class="footer-column" aria-labelledby="footer-links-title">
				<h2 id="footer-links-title">Χρήσιμοι σύνδεσμοι</h2>
				<ul>
					<li><a href="/authors/">Συγγραφείς</a></li>
					<li><a href="https://ichiphost.gr/blog/">Τεχνολογία</a></li>
					<li><a href="https://revcare.gr/el/blog.html">Περιποίηση</a></li>				
				</ul>
			</nav>

			<section class="footer-column" aria-labelledby="footer-contact-title">
				<h2 id="footer-contact-title">Επικοινωνία</h2>
				<address>
					<p>Αθήνα, Ελλάδα</p>
					<p><a href="mailto:hello@enterlife.gr">info@enterlife.gr</a></p>
					<p><a href="tel:+302103250181">+30 2103250181</a></p>
				</address>
				<div class="footer-social" aria-label="Κοινωνικά δίκτυα">
					<a href="https://www.instagram.com/" aria-label="Instagram">in</a>
					<a href="https://www.facebook.com/" aria-label="Facebook">f</a>
					<a href="https://www.pinterest.com/" aria-label="Pinterest">p</a>
				</div>
			</section>

		</div>

		<div class="footer-bottom">
			<p>© {currentYear} Enterlife. Με επιφύλαξη παντός δικαιώματος.</p>
			<a href="#main-content" aria-label="Επιστροφή στην κορυφή">Πάνω ↑</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	.site-footer {
		background: var(--paper-soft);
	}

	.newsletter {
		padding: clamp(1.5rem, 8vw, 3.5rem) 1.5rem;
		background: #ffffff;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.newsletter__inner {
		width: min(46rem, 100%);
		margin-inline: auto;
	}

	.newsletter h2 {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 4vw, 2.35rem);
	}

	.newsletter p:not(.eyebrow) {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		color: var(--muted);
	}

	.newsletter form {
		width: min(39rem, 100%);
		margin-inline: auto;
	}

	.newsletter label {
		display: block;
		width: fit-content;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
	}

	.newsletter__form-row {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
	}

	.newsletter input {
		width: 100%;
		min-height: 3.3rem;
		padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
		border: 1px solid var(--line);
		border-right: 0;
		border-radius: 0;
		background: var(--paper-soft);
		color: var(--ink-deep);
	}

	.newsletter input::placeholder {
		color: #9aa5a7;
	}

	.footer-main {
		padding: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 5rem) 1.5rem 0.5rem;
	}

	.footer-grid {
		display: grid;
		width: min(96rem, 100%);
		margin-inline: auto;
		gap: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 6rem);
		grid-template-columns: 1.25fr 0.9fr 0.9fr 1.15fr;
		display: grid;
		/* Δημιουργία 3 στηλών ίσου πλάτους */
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); 
		/* Κεντράρισμα περιεχομένου οριζόντια */
		justify-items: center; 
		gap: 40px;
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.footer-brand {
		position: relative;
		min-height: 15rem;
	}

	.footer-brand__line-art {
		position: absolute;
		z-index: 0;
		top: -3.5rem;
		left: -2.5rem;
		width: 10rem;
		fill: none;
		opacity: 0.42;
		stroke: #aebbbc;
		stroke-linecap: round;
		stroke-width: 1;
	}

	.footer-brand > *:not(.footer-brand__line-art) {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.footer-brand h2,
	.footer-column h2 {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-size: 1.75rem;
	}

	.footer-brand p,
	.footer-column,
	.footer-column a {
		color: var(--black);
		font-size: 0.96rem;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.footer-brand p {
		max-width: 21rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
	}

	.footer-column ul {
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
		list-style: none;
	}

	.footer-column li + li {
		margin-top: 0.6rem;
	}

	.footer-column a {
		transition: color 160ms ease;
	}

	.footer-column a:hover {
		color: var(--ink-deep);
	}

	address {
		font-style: normal;
	}

	address p {
		margin-bottom: 0.55rem;
	}

	.footer-social {
		display: flex;
		margin-top: 1.25rem;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.footer-social a {
		display: inline-flex;
		width: 2rem;
		height: 2rem;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		border: 1px solid var(--line);
		border-radius: 50%;
		font-family: var(--display);
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.opening-hours {
		margin: 0;
	}

	.opening-hours div {
		display: grid;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		gap: 1rem;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
	}

	.opening-hours dd {
		margin: 0;
		text-align: right;
	}

	.footer-bottom {
		display: flex;
		width: min(56rem, 100%);
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		margin: clamp(2rem, 8vw, 4rem) auto 0;
		padding-top: 0.5rem;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
	}

	.footer-bottom p {
		margin: 0;
	}

	.footer-bottom a {
		display: inline-flex;
		min-width: 3.25rem;
		min-height: 3.25rem;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: var(--blue-deep);
		color: var(--white);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	@media (max-width: 64rem) {
		.footer-grid {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 40rem) {
		.newsletter,
		.footer-main {
			padding-right: 1rem;
			padding-left: 1rem;
		}

		.newsletter__form-row {
			gap: 0.75rem;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.newsletter input {
			border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
		}

		.footer-grid {
			gap: 3rem;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.footer-brand {
			min-height: 0;
		}

		.footer-bottom {
			align-items: flex-start;
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}
	}
</style>
